 towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Keep this property set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLi